Package: mixedStandardization
Type: Package
Title: Standardization for variables of different types (continuous, binary, categorical) in sparse penalized regressions.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xiang Li
Maintainer: The package maintainer <xiangli@gwu.edu>
Description: The package provides 5 standardization methods: Zscore, Gelman, Minmax, Bring, Mixed. The Mixed method is proposed 
    by the author in the paper Standardization of Continuous and Categorical Covariates in Sparse Penalized Regressions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Imports: 
    car,
    caret,
    dplyr,
    stats
